== 評價 ==
我愛羅在系列人氣投票中名列前茅，不斷進入前十名。<ref>{{cite book|last=Kishimoto|first=Masashi|title=Naruto, Volume 28|year=2008|publisher=Viz Media|chapter=Chapter 245|pages=[https://archive.org/details/naruto00kish_2/page/8 8–9]|isbn=978-1-4215-1864-0|chapter-url=https://archive.org/details/naruto00kish_2/page/8}}</ref>上次民調是在2011年，當時我愛羅位居第四。<ref>{{cite book |author=Kishimoto, Masashi|title=Naruto, Volume 56|year=2011|publisher=[[Shueisha|Shueisha]]|chapter=Chapter 531|isbn= 978-1-4215-4207-2}}</ref>多款我愛羅周邊商品已發行，包括他的第一部和第二部外觀的鑰匙圈、毛絨娃娃和可動人偶。{{tsl|en|Anime Central|Anime Central}}將他列為動漫最佳反派第八名，評論集中在閃回畫面解釋他如何成為一個悲劇角色，同時又與[[漩渦鳴人|漩渦鳴人]]相似。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.animecentral.com/news/story.aspx?ID=308|title=Friday Feature|publisher=[[AnimeCentral|AnimeCentral]]|access-date=November 14, 2011|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101013221335/http://animecentral.com/news/story.aspx?ID=308|archive-date=October 13, 2010 }}</ref>2014年，當系列完結時，[[IGN|IGN]]將他列為《[[火影忍者|火影忍者]]》最佳角色第三名。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ign.com/articles/top-10-naruto-characters?page=2 |title=Top Ten Naruto Characters |date=November 12, 2014 |access-date=June 12, 2017 |publisher=[[IGN|IGN]] |url-status=live |archive-url=https://archive.is/20170712135115/http://www.ign.com/articles/top-10-naruto-characters?page=2 |archive-date=July 12, 2017 }}</ref>

動漫和漫畫出版商大多讚揚我愛羅的性格。[[IGN|IGN]]指出我愛羅是“反火影忍者”的，擁有“黑暗、嚴肅的性格”，而非《[[火影忍者|火影忍者]]》慣有的歡呼和興奮。<ref name="IGNNarutoReader">{{cite web|url=http://anime.ign.com/articles/834/834323p4.html|title=IGN: Naruto Reader's Guide|publisher=[[IGN|IGN]]|author=Sparrow, A.E.|date=2007-11-09|access-date=2008-03-04|archive-date=2012-02-20|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/65bYe0SmC?url=http://anime.ign.com/articles/834/834323p4.html|dead-url=yes}}</ref>在另一篇評論中，由於[[鳴人|鳴人]]和我愛羅性格發展的差異，[[IGN|IGN]]還稱我愛羅的過去“情緒化”和“有點令人毛骨悚然”。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://tv.ign.com/articles/767/767826p1.html|title=IGN: An Assassin of the Moonlit Night Review|publisher=[[IGN|IGN]]|author=Van Horn, Jason|date=2007-02-26|access-date=2008-03-04|archive-date=2008-12-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081206101951/http://tv.ign.com/articles/767/767826p1.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>[[動畫新聞網|動畫新聞網]]稱讚[[鳴人|鳴人]]和我愛羅的相似之處為情節增添的“深度和情感”，並評價道“在整個系列中，[[鳴人|鳴人]]的光芒沒有比與我愛羅戰鬥的巔峰時期更耀眼”。<ref name="ANNReviewDVD6">{{cite web|url=http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/review/naruto/dvd-uncut-dvd-box-set-6|title=Naruto Uncut DVD Box Set 6 - Review|publisher=[[Anime_News_Network|Anime News Network]]|author=Martin, Theron|date=February 29, 2008|access-date=2008-03-04|archive-date=2011-06-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110628225311/http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/review/naruto/dvd-uncut-dvd-box-set-6|dead-url=no}}</ref>他們還稱讚[[岸本齊史|岸本]]在漫畫中對我愛羅的視覺呈現，指出“我愛羅裸露出瘋狂的臉令人不寒而栗”。<ref name="ANNNarutoManga8-10">{{cite web|url=http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/review/naruto-gn-8-10|title=Naruto GN 8-10 - Review|publisher=[[Anime_News_Network|Anime News Network]]|author=Kimlinger, Karl|date=2006-11-02|access-date=2008-03-04|archive-date=2018-06-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180617084631/https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/review/naruto-gn-8-10|dead-url=no}}</ref>Mania Entertainment指出，我愛羅和[[宇智波佐助|佐助]]的第一次戰鬥表明，儘管態度很暴力，我愛羅卻有著“脆弱”的心理。他的過去也受到Mania Entertainment稱讚，因為它包含“大量合理的情感”，讓觀眾能夠更了解我愛羅的個性。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.mania.com/naruto-box-set-06-also-wspecial-edition_article_79870.html |title=Naruto Box Set 06 (also w/special edition) |publisher=Mania Entertainment |author=Rich, Justin |date=June 18, 2008 |access-date=September 15, 2009 |url-status=dead |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111214233412/http://www.mania.com/naruto-box-set-06-also-wspecial-edition_article_79870.html |archive-date=December 14, 2011 }}</ref>{{tsl|en|DVD Talk||DVD Talk}}作家小陶德·道格拉斯喜歡我愛羅和[[鳴人|鳴人]]之間的相似之處，以及前者被後者擊敗後的心境。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.dvdtalk.com/reviews/33010/naruto-uncut-boxed-set-volume-7-special-edition/|title=Naruto Uncut Boxed Set, Volume 7 (Special Edition)|publisher=DVD Talk|author=Douglass Jr.; Todd|access-date=July 5, 2017|date=April 21, 2008|archive-date=2021-08-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210801044921/https://www.dvdtalk.com/reviews/33010/naruto-uncut-boxed-set-volume-7-special-edition/|dead-url=no}}</ref>我愛羅回歸支援木葉忍者戰鬥，受到Active Anime的Holly Ellingwood稱讚，她主要關注我愛羅的內心變化。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.activeanime.com/html/content/view/3983/57/ |title=NARUTO UNCUT BOX SET 10 LIMITED EDITION (ADVANCE REVIEW) |publisher=Active Anime |author=Ellingwood, Holly |date=October 10, 2008 |access-date=July 5, 2017 |url-status=dead |archive-url=https://archive.li/20110707081528/http://www.activeanime.com/html/content/view/3983/57/ |archive-date=July 7, 2011 }}</ref>我愛羅的英文聲優[[利亞姆·奧布萊恩|利亞姆·奧布萊恩]]獲得好評。[[IGN|IGN]]指出，他做了“出色的工作”，使我愛羅聽起來令觀眾害怕，<ref name="IGNEpisodeGaaraIdentityReview">{{cite web|url=http://tv.ign.com/articles/763/763656p1.html|title=IGN: Astonishing Truth! Gaara's Identity Emerges! Review|publisher=[[IGN|IGN]]|author=Van Horn, Jason|date=2007-02-12|access-date=2008-03-04|archive-date=2008-02-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080202121124/http://tv.ign.com/articles/763/763656p1.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>[[動畫新聞網|動畫新聞網]]指出他是該系列中最好的聲優之一。<ref name="ANNReviewDVD6"/>

在系列第二部中，我愛羅從砂忍晉升為領導者，被Mania Entertainment的Briana Lawrence認為是該系列中最令人驚訝的發展。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.mania.com/naruto-vol-28_article_83777.html |title=Naruto Vol. #28 |publisher=Mania Entertainment |author=Lawrence, Briana |date=February 27, 2008 |access-date=November 17, 2011 |url-status=dead |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121025193834/http://www.mania.com/naruto-vol-28_article_83777.html |archive-date=October 25, 2012 }}</ref>UK Anime Network的Kevin Leathers表示，雖然在系列的第一部中，我愛羅是可怕的反派，但在接下來的部分中，他變得“更加立體”。<ref name="ukanim">{{cite web|url=http://www.uk-anime.net/anime/Naruto_Shippuden_Box_Set_1.html|title=Anime Review: Naruto Shippuden Box Set 1|publisher=UK Anime Network|author=Leathers, Kevin|date=July 19, 2010|access-date=November 17, 2011|archive-date=2012-03-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120320000733/http://www.uk-anime.net/anime/Naruto_Shippuden_Box_Set_1.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>同樣地，Douglass Jr.稱讚《[[火影忍者疾風傳|火影忍者疾風傳]]》中我愛羅的發展，因為他與[[鳴人|鳴人]]的關係有了擴展。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.dvdtalk.com/reviews/42122/naruto-shippuden-8/|title=Naruto Shippuden, Vol. 8|publisher=[[DVD_Talk|DVD Talk]]|author=Douglass Jr., Todd|date=April 6, 2010|access-date=November 17, 2011|archive-date=2010-05-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100507031247/http://www.dvdtalk.com/reviews/42122/naruto-shippuden-8/|dead-url=no}}</ref>他與[[地達羅|地達羅]]的戰鬥也得到了積極反應，評論家稱讚我愛羅的招式和兩位忍者採用的策略。<ref name="ukanim"/><ref>{{cite web|url=http://comics.ign.com/articles/848/848479p1.html|title=Naruto Vol. 28 Review|publisher=IGN|author=Sparrow, A.E.|date=January 29, 2008|access-date=November 17, 2011|archive-date=2012-02-01|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/658E8HJP2?url=http://comics.ign.com/articles/848/848479p1.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>另一方面，來自[[動畫新聞網|動畫新聞網]]的{{tsl|en|Jason Thompson (writer)|Jason Thompson}}指出，雖然我愛羅自從在第一部出現後一直在發展，由於他以前有殺人的願望，後來被接受為新任風影總感覺是錯誤的。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/house-of-1000-manga/2014-11-13/naruto-part-ii/.80991|title=House of 1000 Manga - Naruto Part II|publisher=Anime News Network|author=Thompson, Jason|date=November 13, 2014|access-date=November 14, 2014|archive-date=2017-04-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170428143850/http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/house-of-1000-manga/2014-11-13/naruto-part-ii/.80991|dead-url=no}}</ref>在第二部的最後幾集動畫中，同樣來自[[動畫新聞網|動畫新聞網]]的Amy McNulty喜歡我愛羅與其他經常出現的角色一起作為喜劇人物來處理。儘管如此，與第二部早期故事情節相比，她發現我愛羅現在將[[鳴人|鳴人]]視為朋友而非英雄，這一點很重要。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/review/naruto-shippuden/episode-497/.112942|title=Naruto Shippuden Episode 497|publisher=Anime News Network|author=McNulty, Amy|date=March 4, 2017|access-date=July 7, 2017|archive-date=2021-08-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210801044924/https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/review/naruto-shippuden/episode-497/.112942|dead-url=no}}</ref>

